column5: Every feature-length movie I watched in 2022. My third year of keeping track of how many movies I've watched. In 2020 I watched 375, in 2021 I watched 237; I can't wait to find out how many I'll watch this year. For both of the prior years, I ended up with a first watch/rewatch ratio of about 2:1. I think if I had a goal for this year it would be to lessen the amount of rewatches and focus on watching things I've never seen before.
